# Running the Birthday App with Docker Compose

Follow these steps to run the app using Docker Compose:

## Prerequisites

- [Docker](https://docs.docker.com/get-docker/) installed
- [Docker Compose](https://docs.docker.com/compose/install/) installed

## Steps

1. **Clone the repository** (if you haven't already):

    ```bash
    git clone https://github.com/saldhyyoga/birthday-app
    cd birthday-app
    ```

2. **Start the app:**

    ```bash
    docker-compose up
    ```

    To run in detached mode:

    ```bash
    docker-compose up -d
    ```

3. **Access the app:**

    Open your browser and go to [http://localhost:3000]

5. **Stop the app:**

    Press `Ctrl+C` or run:

    ```bash
    docker-compose down
    ```

---